{"tid":303827,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平：年輕人要報效香港及祖國","createTime":"2017-06-30T12:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T16:21:48.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"92832575dee44011e78d463b72b38a6262b61ebf","tid":303827,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:39:48.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】國家主席習近平到八鄉少年警訊活動中心與青年交流。<br />\n<br />\n習近平在約早上11時抵達八鄉少年警訊活動中心，在行政長官梁振英等陪同下，觀看營內正進行的領導才能及體能訓練，並與在場的少年警訊成員交談。<br />\n<br />\n習近平指，很關心青年的未來，勉勵年輕人要報效香港及祖國，其後逐一與他們握手及拍照。<br />\n<br />\n警務處處長盧偉聰及少年警訊成員分別向習近平介紹中心內的設施，及少年警訊的歷史及背景。盧偉聰又向習近平表示，現時香港犯罪率是最低的一年，並感謝內地公安部的支持。<br />\n<br />\n習近平逗留約四十分鐘後離開，在活動中心外保安森嚴，有大批警員駐守，有衝鋒隊警員巡邏，警方早上亦在粉錦公路一帶實施封路。"},{"pid":"afed5f0a1db2b6cb71f6bf5facc66a829d46c0ad","tid":303827,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:40:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=226719\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D226719&d=%2FlaCnGdCtg1auBaOPR6qUGowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=5219bb3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D226719&h=d2b886c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=226719</a>"},{"pid":"cc41ad475c9399ec4965becb6cfd8c35254fd7f1","tid":303827,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010454f2e0bad705064d29476bc4032251657554","tid":303827,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:49:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0b18797c87468393fec7edec1b0dfcc7eef1ee5","tid":303827,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:50:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜都冇俾過我點解要報效</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為國家付出<br />\n比當房你住都要感恩"},{"pid":"4fca99bd061c5b11ea3089